## Step 3: Verify the initial value of accounts payable
Since all of these transactions occurred on 2023-12-31, they represent the initial setup of accounts payable at the beginning of our accounting period. In this case, the initial value would be 1,240,000.00.

However, I need to consider if there were any accounts payable balances before these purchases. Since there are no transactions before 2023-12-31 in the data, and the first entries appear to be initiating the accounts, I'll assume the initial accounts payable before these purchases was 0.
